snippet.title: CONTRA: ROGUE CORPS Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
A new installment to the Contra franchise is here! Join the most resilient team, the CONTRA: ROGUE CORPS, in an action-packed, run-and-gun frenzy!
Defeat the aliens and save the world!

Offical Website:
https://www.konami.com/games/contra/rc/
